Package de.oth.blocklib.world.vegetation.trees

Class JungleBiomTree

java.lang.Object
de.oth.blocklib.world.vegetation.trees.BiomTree
de.oth.blocklib.world.vegetation.trees.JungleBiomTree
public class JungleBiomTree
extends BiomTree
This class is a subclass of BiomTree. It creates a standard tree for the Jungle. This class will also only be created in the Jungle Biom.
